    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new companion for the road? I\u2019m parting with my absolute favorite car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really wonderful shape\u2014well-maintained, super clean, and it runs like a total dream. It\u2019s got a few tiny signs of love from the years, but it still looks fantastic and is ready for so many more adventures. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come by and take it for a spin, you'll love how it handles!",
