    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec driver\u2019s car featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-Differential lock. The chassis is structurally sound, featuring essential rear subframe reinforcement and an upgraded suspension setup with Bilstein dampers for improved lateral stability. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent valve adjustment and rod bearing service. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain razor-sharp, offering a visceral analog driving experience that modern performance cars fail to replicate.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
