      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me every single day. It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being well-loved but still looking and feeling great on the road. Whether you're zipping through your daily commute or heading out on a fun weekend road trip, this car is totally ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a great home!",
      "price": 34500.0,
